column5: big sale at gagnons from today till the tenth was a zoo today half hour in line to check out and pay lol but got a gloomis rod for less than half price and broke down and bought a abu rocket no tax on the reel and a 30 dollar mail in rebate
was just there, picked up a shimano selus UL rod for my daughter to start fishing this year
awesome ...... pass on the passion but dont blame her when she wants a boat for christmas

awesome ...... pass on the passion but dont blame her when she wants a boat for christmas   i have an inflatable paddle boat with 2 rod holders.  just looking for an electric motor to put on the back of it.  can hold up to a 4hp gas motor too.  can't wait for warmer weather!
